    • Class com.authlete.common.dto.AuthorizationIssueRequest extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      6L

      • Serialized Fields

        • ticket

          String ticket
          The ticket issued by Authlete's endpoint.

        • subject

          String subject
          The subject (end-user) managed by the service.

        • authTime

          long authTime
          The time when the end-user was authenticated.

        • acr

          String acr
          The authentication context class reference.

        • claims

          String claims
          Claims in JSON format.

        • properties

          Property[] properties
          Extra properties to associate with an access token and/or an authorization code.

        • scopes

          String[] scopes
          Scopes to associate with an access token and/or an authorization code. If this field is null, the scopes specified in the original authorization request from the client application are used. In other cases, including the case of an empty array, the scopes here will replace the original scopes contained in the original request.
